text: George Richardson (28 May 1834 - 1 May 1911) was an Australian cricketer. He played two first-class matches for New South Wales between 1859/60 and 1860/61. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1834 births Category:1911 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers
title: George Richardson (cricketer)
